  "text": "Pasquini et al. designed an empirical system to verify online news by analyzing images from news article. The system identified the set of meta-data visuals related to the same topic and presented some common visual elements. After that, the data set was compared with many websites with the same topic. Thus, the system the could differentiate between the images and output the fake one [CITATION_1] .",
